{"tid":767249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無法無天】醫院門外黑幫尋仇 警拉6男1女扣6車","createTime":"2018-08-04T10:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:33:24.000Z","uid":99004,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"29edbdf4cea1b269b005740d31cf21288000c1e0","tid":767249,"uid":99004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180804/large/1533350558_1ae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180804%2Flarge%2F1533350558_1ae1.jpg&h=ea62b2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北角和富道76號一間餐廳，昨晚9時許，警方接報有人打架。兩名男子因為租務金錢問題爭執，其中姓霍(49歲)男子遇襲被推跌臉受傷，他在場姓沙(54歲)的朋友勸止也同告遇襲，手受傷。警員到場將兩人送院，並拘捕涉嫌傷人姓劉(46歲)的男子。<br />\n<br />\n不料，當傷者送抵東區醫院時，已有10多人分乘6輛私家車在急症室門外「恭候」。兩人被圍毆，要警員喝止。逞兇者隨即四散，東區醫院對面柴灣警署的警員增援趕到，在場拘捕數名男女，餘人逃去無蹤。警方經調查後，在香港仔區再拘捕數名人士，共5男1女(22至64歲)涉嫌傷人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n東區反黑組探員其後到場，調查兇徒遺下的私家車，在車上撿獲壘球棍。其間1名紋身男子乘的士到來醫院，探員覺有可疑截查，懷疑他與案有關，帶走調查。警方並將涉案私家車拖走。<br />\n<br />\n至於該兩名傷者，經敷治後1人已出院。警方懷疑事件涉及黑幫尋仇，部分人士有三合會背景，正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180804/58522194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58522194&d=FGY%2FvSnesoFgnZVOdr3729Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=dcc26dbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58522194&h=34557fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180804/58522194</a><br />\n<br />\n條腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02996f94663b7ef0efc9fdd072f91fa5ac3f8fd6","tid":767249,"uid":18465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"有紋身就有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fc120757190499beb1127aad8f029f4ec88b84","tid":767249,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"R35 nismo?<br />\n配呢對腳差唔多"},{"pid":"48aa6cbfcb81da53ea9bb6e479834f79b3353daa","tid":767249,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ab7b76e950542d1d97319543dc91e9697d4d410","tid":767249,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02996f94663b7ef0efc9fdd072f91fa5ac3f8fd6","tid":767249,"uid":18465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"有紋身就有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"華人社會好正常"},{"pid":"42702a5d2e30bfd9d6fc39d2ccc76c1c83e4e290","tid":767249,"uid":103936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"傻撚左<br />\n醫院對面就係醫署都仲黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a270b98e3cce1c8d41693d0a5ed895eba1ce2ee3","tid":767249,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42702a5d2e30bfd9d6fc39d2ccc76c1c83e4e290","tid":767249,"uid":103936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"傻撚左<br />\n醫院對面就係醫署都仲黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"威呀"}]}